  "code": "sequenceDiagram\n    participant Device as IoT Device<br/>(MCU + TPM)\n    participant Factory as Manufacturer<br/>(Secure Facility)\n    participant Owner as Owner/Operator<br/>(Enterprise)\n    participant Registry as DID Registry<br/>(Public Ledger)\n\n    Note over Device, Factory: Manufacturing Phase\n    \n    Factory->>Device: 1. Inject Identity Key (EK)\n    Device->>Factory: 2. Return Public EK\n    Factory->>Registry: 3. Register Reference (SerialNumber -> PubKey)\n    \n    Note over Device, Owner: Onboarding Phase\n    \n    Owner->>Device: 4. Power On & Connect\n    Device->>Device: 5. Generate Attestation Key (AK)\n    Device->>Owner: 6. Send Attestation (Quote(AK) signed by EK)\n    \n    Owner->>Registry: 7. Verify EK Trust Chain\n    Registry-->>Owner: Valid Manufacturer\n    \n    Owner->>Device: 8. Issue Root PoA (Bind AK to Owner DID)\n    Device->>Device: 9. Store PoA in Secure Flash\n    \n    Note right of Device: Device is now<br/>Authorized Agent\n",
